      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is currently not roadworthy. It requires extensive mechanical repairs, including significant engine diagnostics and likely a transmission overhaul. The exterior shows heavy wear with substantial rust on the rocker panels, fading clear coat, and several deep scratches. Inside, the upholstery is torn and the electronics are inconsistent. This is strictly a project car for someone with the tools and time to perform a full restoration.",
